    <entry>
      <title>Hexo之Next主题配置</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/23/hexo/Hexo%E4%B9%8BNext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/23/hexo/Hexo%E4%B9%8BNext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo之Next主题配置"><a href="#Hexo之Next主题配置" class="headerlink" title="Hexo之Next主题配置"></a>Hexo之Next主题配置</h1><h2 id="为什么是Next"><a href="#为什么是Next" class="headerlink" title="为什么是Next"></a>为什么是Next</h2><p>​以下是基于GitHub做的Hexo各大主题Star、下载量分析，仅供参考</p><table><thead><tr><th>Name</th><th>Star</th><th>Downloads</th><th>Proportion</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>NexT</td><td>12k</td><td>200k</td><td>40%</td></tr><tr><td>Landscape</td><td>8k</td><td>120k</td><td>20%</td></tr><tr><td>Light</td><td>4k</td><td>80k</td><td>10%</td></tr><tr><td>Minos</td><td>2k</td><td>40k</td><td>5%</td></tr><tr><td>Apollo</td><td>1k</td><td>20k</td><td>3%</td></tr><tr><td>Others</td><td>5k</td><td>100k</td><td>22%</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="Next主题简介"><a href="#Next主题简介" class="headerlink" title="Next主题简介"></a>Next主题简介</h2><p>​Hexo NexT主题是一款非常受欢迎、功能强大的Hexo主题，由Next.Mistaken大神开发。该主题具有响应式设计、多种布局、多种配色方案、多种插件等特点，使得它非常适合用于个人博客、技术博客、科技博客等各类博客网站。同时，Hexo NexT主题还支持多种第三方评论系统、社交分享、代码高亮等功能，为用户提供了更好的使用体验。因此，该主题受到了广大用户的喜爱和追捧。</p><hr><blockquote><p> 以下整理均源自：<a href="https://theme-next.js.org/">NexT - Theme for Hexo (theme-next.js.org)</a></p></blockquote><h2 id="安装Next"><a href="#安装Next" class="headerlink" title="安装Next"></a>安装Next</h2><p>下载 NexT 有两种推荐的方法任选其一即可。<br>首先在命令行中将 dir 更改为博客根目录，然后继续执行以下步骤。</p><ol><li>NPM<br><code>npm install hexo-theme-next@latest</code></li><li>Git<br><code>git clone https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next themes/next</code></li></ol><h2 id="Next配置"><a href="#Next配置" class="headerlink" title="Next配置"></a>Next配置</h2><ol><li><p>建议将node_modules&#x2F;hexo-theme-next&#x2F;_config.yml 文件复制到站点根目录并重命名为 _config.next.yml<br>原因：通过 git 或 npm 升级 NexT 主题时，配置文件会被覆盖，这给主题的配置带来不便，但是此方法需确保您使用的是 Hexo 5.0 或更高版本</p></li><li><p>启用Next<br>修改站点目录下的 _config.yml(以下均是)文件，将 theme: landscape 修改为 theme: next</p></li><li><p>设置缓存支持<br>NexT v6+允许缓存内容生成。将 NexT 配置文件(站点根目录下的 _config.next.yml)中的值设置为 true</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Allow to cache content generation.</span><br><span class="line"># 缓存支持</span><br><span class="line">cache:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>方案选择<br>方案是NexT支持的一项功能，通过使用Scheme，NexT为您提供不同的视图。几乎所有的配置都可以被这些方案使用。到目前为止，NexT支持4种方案，它们是：</p><ul><li>Muse→默认方案，这是NexT的初始版本。使用黑白色调，主要看起来干净。</li><li><code>Mist</code>→ Muse的紧凑版本，具有整洁的单列视图。</li><li><code>Pisces</code>→双列方案，像邻居的女儿一样新鲜。</li><li><code>Gemini</code>→ 看起来像双鱼座，但具有带有阴影的不同列块，以显示对视图更敏感。</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#scheme: Muse</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">scheme: Gemini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置菜单项<br>菜单设置项的格式包含 3 个值：<code>Key: /link/ || icon</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>Values</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Key</td><td>菜单名称(区分大小写)</td></tr><tr><td>link</td><td>网站对应的文件夹</td></tr><tr><td>icon</td><td>图标</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: / || fa fa-home</span><br><span class="line">  archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">  Docs:</span><br><span class="line">    default: /docs/ || fa fa-book</span><br><span class="line">    Getting Started:</span><br><span class="line">      default: /getting-started/ || fa fa-flag</span><br><span class="line">      Installation: /installation.html || fa fa-download</span><br><span class="line">      Configuration: /configuration.html || fa fa-wrench</span><br><span class="line">    Third Party Plugins:</span><br><span class="line">      default: /third-party-services/ || fa fa-puzzle-piece</span><br><span class="line">      Math Equations: /math-equations.html || fa fa-square-root-alt</span><br><span class="line">      Comment Systems: /comments.html || fa fa-comment-alt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>每个子菜单项都需要一个<code>default</code>页面。</p></blockquote><p>默认情况下，NexT 显示不带徽章的菜单项的图标，如需要请做如下配置。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu_settings:</span><br><span class="line">  icons: true</span><br><span class="line">  # 将值设置为以显示 NexT 配置文件部分中菜单项中的帖子/类别/标签计数</span><br><span class="line">  badges: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>侧边栏样式<br>默认情况下，侧边栏仅显示在帖子中（具有目录），并放置在左侧。您可以通过编辑 NexT 配置文件中设置下的值来更改它。<code>sidebar</code><br><code>position</code>:设置侧边栏位置，left-左侧，right-右侧<br><code>width</code>:通过以像素为单位指定设置来更改侧边栏宽度，width: 300<br><code>display</code>:具体什么时候显示侧边栏</p><ul><li><code>post</code>→具有索引的帖子中显示侧边栏。</li><li><code>always</code>→ 在所有页面中显示侧边栏。</li><li><code>hide</code>→ 在所有页面中隐藏它（但可以由用户手动打开）。</li><li><code>remove</code>→ 完全删除侧边栏。</li></ul><p><code>padding</code>:通过更改以下值来设置侧边栏填充（以像素为单位），padding: 18<br><code>offset</code>:通过更改以下值来设置侧边栏与顶部菜单栏的偏移量（以像素为单位），offset: 12</p></li><li><p>配置头像<br>默认情况下，NexT 不会在侧边栏中显示头像。可以通过编辑 NexT 配置文件中<code>avatar</code>的值来配置它。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">avatar:</span><br><span class="line">  url: /images/avatar.gif # 头像位置，支持网路链接</span><br><span class="line">  rounded: true # true-圆形，false-方形</span><br><span class="line">  rotated: true# true-头像在鼠标悬停下旋转，false-不旋转</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>其他站点<br>默认情况下，NexT 在侧边栏中显示帖子&#x2F;类别&#x2F;标签的类别和计数。您可以通过编辑 NexT 配置文件中的值来配置它。<code>site_state</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">site_state: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>侧边栏社交链接<br>默认情况下，NexT在侧边栏中显示社交链接的图标。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">social:</span><br><span class="line">  GitHub: https://github.com/yourname || fab fa-github</span><br><span class="line">  E-Mail: mailto:yourname@gmail.com || fa fa-envelope</span><br><span class="line">  Weibo: https://weibo.com/yourname || fab fa-weibo</span><br><span class="line">  #Twitter: https://twitter.com/yourname || fab fa-twitter</span><br><span class="line">  #FB Page: https://www.facebook.com/yourname || fab fa-facebook</span><br><span class="line">  #StackOverflow: https://stackoverflow.com/yourname || fab fa-stack-overflow</span><br><span class="line">  #YouTube: https://youtube.com/yourname || fab fa-youtube</span><br><span class="line">  #Instagram: https://instagram.com/yourname || fab fa-instagram</span><br><span class="line">  #Skype: skype:yourname?call|chat || fab fa-skype</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>页脚图标<br>默认情况下，NexT 在页脚中显示带有年份和版权信息之间的动画的红色图标。您可以通过编辑 NexT 配置文件部分中的值来配置它。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">footer:</span><br><span class="line">  icon:</span><br><span class="line">    name: fa fa-user # 图标名称</span><br><span class="line">    animated: false # 图标动画</span><br><span class="line">    color: &quot;#808080&quot; # 图标颜色</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>发布字数统计<br>安装插件：在站点根目录目录中执行以下命令进行安装<br><code>npm install hexo-word-counter</code><br>激活：修改Hexo配置文件(_config.yml)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 字数统计</span><br><span class="line">symbols_count_time:</span><br><span class="line">  symbols: true # 字数统计</span><br><span class="line">  time: true  # 阅读时间建议</span><br><span class="line">  total_symbols: true # 所有文章的字数</span><br><span class="line">  total_time: true  # 所有帖子的估计阅读时间</span><br><span class="line">  awl: 4  # 平均字长（字符数以字为单位）</span><br><span class="line">  wpm: 275  # 每分钟的平均字数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Next主题文件配置：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">symbols_count_time:</span><br><span class="line">  # 默认情况下，NexT 以单独的行显示单词计数和估计阅读时间。您可以通过在 NexT 配置文件中设置 value 将它们添加到一行中</span><br><span class="line">  separated_meta: true</span><br><span class="line">  # 默认情况下，NexT 不会在页脚部分中显示字数和估计阅读时间的文本说明。您可以通过在 NexT 配置文件中将值设置为来启用它。</span><br><span class="line">  item_text_total: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>热门文章<br>安装插件：在站点根目录目录中执行以下命令进行安装<br><code>npm install hexo-related-posts</code><br>修改主题配置文件：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">related_posts:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>代码块样式</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">codeblock:</span><br><span class="line">  # Code Highlight theme</span><br><span class="line">  # All available themes: https://theme-next.js.org/highlight/</span><br><span class="line">  theme:</span><br><span class="line">    light: default</span><br><span class="line">    dark: stackoverflow-dark</span><br><span class="line">  prism:</span><br><span class="line">    light: prism</span><br><span class="line">    dark: prism-dark</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>返回首页</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">back2top:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  sidebar: true#将值设置为 将按钮放在边栏中</span><br><span class="line">  scrollpercent: true#按钮中显示滚动百分比标签</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>阅读进度<br>NexT支持页面滚动阅读进度指示器。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reading_progress:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: left | right</span><br><span class="line">  start_at: left</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: top | bottom</span><br><span class="line">  position: top</span><br><span class="line">  reversed: false</span><br><span class="line">  color: &quot;#37c6c0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  height: 2px</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
